headline.main: No. 12 Texas Women Beat Oklahoma St in Big 12 Tournament
headline.print_headline: No. 12 Texas Women Beat Oklahoma St in Big 12 Tournament

lead_paragraph: Brooke McCarty led four Texas players in double figures with 13 points and the No. 12 Longhorns beat Oklahoma State 71-60 on Saturday night in the quarterfinals of the Big 12 Conference Tournament.
